(Trigger): PlayerMessage

IfThenElse
  If
    $message
    =
    /kit {name}
Then
+ Commands
/kit give $player {kit name, you need to create one before you use command}

For Advanced Role Kits use this:


IfThenElse
  If
    $playerRole
    =
    {role you want to only be able to use /kit}
Then

+ IfThenElse
  If
    $message
    =
    /kit {name}
 Then
 
 + Commands
 
